OL,3,C'I stabbed the guy' - Moment murderer
OL,4,Cis arrested after killing friend
OL,6,FA Bristol man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering his friend after a body-worn
OL,8,Fcamera recorded him telling officers
OL,9,F'I stabbed the guy'.
OL,11,FLee Llewellyn used a knife to kill 32-
OL,12,Fyear-old Martin Hefferman, from
OL,13,FFishponds, at a house in Honeysuckle
OL,14,FClose, Bradley Stoke during the early
OL,15,Fhours of Saturday 18 November 2023.
OL,17,FLlewellyn had denied one count of
OL,18,Fmurder, claiming Martin had
OL,19,Faccidentally jumped onto the knife.
OL,20,FBut he was convicted by jurors after a
OL,21,Fnine-day trial at Bristol Crown Court.
