OL,3,C'I stabbed the guy' - Moment murderer
OL,4,Cis arrested after killing friend
OL,6,FThe 51-year-old, of Froomshaw Road in
OL,7,FBristol, will be sentenced on Friday
OL,8,F24 May.
OL,10,FThe jury was told Llewellyn and Mr
OL,11,FHefferman had been at the address with
OL,12,Ftwo women for approximately 48 hours
OL,13,Fbefore the stabbing, during which time
OL,14,Falcohol and drugs were consumed.
OL,16,FNeither of the women saw the fatal
OL,17,Fstabbing, but they told police they
OL,18,Fhad heard an argument between the two
OL,19,Fmen downstairs shortly beforehand.
OL,20,FThey then found Mr Hefferman bleeding
OL,21,Fand critically injured on the landing.
