OL,6,FOne of the women called police at
OL,7,Fapproximately 3.20am and the first
OL,8,Fofficers arrived approximately 10
OL,9,Fminutes later.
OL,11,FLlewellyn told those officers he had
OL,12,F'stabbed the guy' and he had sustained
OL,13,Frib injuries in an altercation with Mr
OL,14,FHefferman before picking up the knife.
OL,16,FOn being transported to the police
OL,17,Fcar, he said he hoped Mr Hefferman
OL,18,Fsurvived because he did not want "no
OL,19,Fmurder charge". He also said: "I
OL,20,Fdidn't mean to do it but he attacked
OL,21,Fme."
