OL,6,FWhen in custody though he replied "no
OL,7,Fcomment" to all questions.
OL,9,FIn court, Llewellyn claimed the death
OL,10,Fwas as a result of an accident.
OL,12,FA pathologist's report concluded Mr
OL,13,FHefferman died of a single stab wound
OL,14,Fto his upper chest, damaging his heart.
OL,16,FThe prosecution argued the severity of
OL,17,Finjury and the location of the wound
OL,18,Fshowed Llewellyn intended to kill or
OL,19,Fcause Mr Hefferman very serious injury.
