OL,6,FDetective Inspector Mark Newbury, of
OL,7,Fthe Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It's clear there was a dispute
OL,9,Fbetween Lee Llewellyn and Martin
OL,10,FHefferman in the moments before the
OL,11,Fmurder took place.
OL,13,F"Whatever caused that argument cannot
OL,14,Fjustify the conscious decision
OL,15,FLlewellyn made to grab a knife, which
OL,16,Fhe used to kill Martin.
