OL,6,F"It may have been a decision made in
OL,7,Fthe heat of the moment, but it is
OL,8,Finconceivable he would not have
OL,9,Frecognised bringing a knife into the
OL,10,Fargument could have tragic
OL,11,Fconsequences. Sadly, that proved the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,F"He then made several telling
OL,15,Fadmissions to police after being
OL,16,Farrested.
OL,18,F"Martin was a young man whose life was
OL,19,Fsnatched away from him on that fateful
OL,20,Fday six months ago.
